n>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">写切流 分为四步</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">1）首先验证 写新库没问题 相当于对新加代码进行灰度 如果有问题 进行回切</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">2）当验证写新库没问题，需要补齐数据库数据</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">3）当数据补齐后 转换为主写新库</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #3e3e3e;letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">4）后续如果读写新库都没问题 可以彻底下线旧库存</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n         <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/82dcf759-e43e-4684-f831-fd7f4c11f100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39444444444444443\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100146711\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/82dcf759-e43e-4684-f831-fd7f4c11f100/public\">\n        </section>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n       </section>\n       <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <section style=\"margin-top: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\n         <section style=\"background-color:rgb(19, 139, 222);padding-bottom:2px;text-align:center;\">\n          <section style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);border-top-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-right-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);border-left-color: rgb(19, 139, 222);padding: 0.5em 1.5em;\">\n           <p style=\"line-height: 20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">四、总结</span></strong></span></p>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <section style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: normal;line-height: 1.6em;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文详细梳理了线上生产环境的全流程，包括迁移和切换的灰度方案对比。在数据源选型方面，根据实际业务需求选择合适的中间件是整个工作的基石。在代码改造和数据异构方面，选择恰当的设计模式和合理的架构方案是关键所在。存量数据迁移和增量数据同步是不可或缺的步骤。上线过程中，确保系统具备可监控、可回滚和可灰度的能力，是实现平滑切换的保障。</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n       </section>\n       <section data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">\n        <section style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);padding-left:0.5em;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;padding-right:0.5em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者丨即时零售 杨亚龙</span></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);padding-left:0.5em;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;padding-right:0.5em;text-align:left;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源丨公众号：京东技术（ID：jingdongjishu）</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);padding-left:0.5em;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;padding-right:0.5em;\">\n         <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">dbaplus社群欢迎广大技术人员投稿，投稿邮箱：</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">editor@dbaplus.cn</span></span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a065bf86-b2ca-48ba-ec6f-9115bcf88400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100146161\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a065bf86-b2ca-48ba-ec6f-9115bcf88400/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/716ff43c-31cf-4594-a5d7-f9348cfaef00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100130225\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/716ff43c-31cf-4594-a5d7-f9348cfaef00/public\">\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文详细介绍了将线上生产环境 MongoDB 数据库平滑迁移至 JImKV、MySQL 和 ES 的完整流程和灰度方案，保障业务连续性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文详细介绍了将线上生产环境 MongoDB 数据库平滑迁移至 JImKV、MySQL 和 ES 的完整流程和灰度方案，保障业务连续性。",
  "summary": "本文详细回顾了一次将线上生产环境的 MongoDB 数据库迁移到其他介质的完整流程，旨在解决 MongoDB 存储的瓶颈/成本问题。该系统使用 MongoDB 存储核心数据，采用 1 主 1 副本模式。迁移方案包括：梳理迁移范围、确定数据存储介质、改造 DAO 层、双写数据并迁移、通过 R2 流量回放进行数据一致性校验的验证/测试回归/数据比对，以及切量。文章重点介绍了代码改造和数据异构的方法，采用装饰器模式统一控制双写和切量逻辑。针对存量和增量数据，分别制定了迁移和同步方案。最后，详细阐述了上线过程中的监控、灰度和回滚策略，确保系统平滑切换，最终成功实现了数据库的平滑迁移，保障了线上业务的稳定运行。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "采用装饰器模式统一控制双写逻辑和切量逻辑。",
      "explanation": "通过装饰器模式，可以避免对现有业务逻辑的侵入，实现平滑过渡和灵活切换，降低改造风险。"
    },
    {
      "point": "增量数据同步采用先写 MongoDB 再写 MySQL，通过 MQ 异步补偿。",
      "explanation": "保证数据最终一致性，降低因 MySQL 写入失败导致的数据丢失风险，提高系统的可靠性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "上线过程需具备可监控、可回滚和可灰度的能力。",
      "explanation": "通过监控及时发现问题，灰度发布控制影响范围，回滚机制保障系统快速恢复，确保平滑切换。"
    },
    {
      "point": "根据业务需求和数据特点选择合适的中间件作为数据源。",
      "explanation": "数据源的选型是整个迁移工作的基石，合适的中间件能够更好地满足业务需求，提升系统性能。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
